Dear {!RW_Booking__r.Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!

We are pleased to inform you that the sanction for your home loan application has been approved and the details have been updated in our system.

Please find the key sanction details below for your reference:

Unit Number: {!RW_Booking__r.Unit_No__r.Name}
Sanction Bank: {!RW_Bank_Name__c}
Sanction Amount: {!RW_Sanction_Amount__c}
Sanction Date: {!RW_Sanction_Date__c}
Sanction Document Number: {{Sanction_Document_Number}}

You can also view the complete sanction details on your Runwal app: {!$Label.App_Link}

If you require any clarification or assistance, our home loan team will be happy to support you.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
{!$Label.Support_Email} | {!$Label.Support_Phone}
